caption: A cozy living room with a long yellow sofa in front of a wall of bookshelves, two children and an adult relaxing on the couch, and a happy dog sitting in the middle.
final_prompt: A cozy, well-lit living room scene with a long bright yellow sofa facing the viewer, backed by an extensive wall of neatly arranged bookshelves filled with books. Two children and one adult are comfortably seated on the sofa, appearing relaxed and content. In the center of the sofa cushions, a happy dog sits, looking towards the camera. The room is bathed in warm ambient light, creating a homely and inviting atmosphere. The image style is realistic with balanced colors and soft shadows to evoke a sense of warmth and family comfort.

Soft natural light floods the room through unseen windows, creating a peaceful and inviting atmosphere. The style is realistic with rich textures and warm tones, emphasizing comfort and family bonding.
